spec_data.Name: perl-Module-Starter-Plugin-CGIApp
spec_data.Description:
This is a plugin for Module::Starter that builds you a skeleton
CGI::Application module with all the extra files needed to package it for
CPAN. You can customize the output using HTML::Template.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:34:25 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Template based module starter for CGI apps
